---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import '../styles/pages/home.css';
---

<Layout
    title="Uzzala Bio Energy Solutions — Bio CBG Technology with Innovation"
    description="Uzzala Bio Energy Solutions specializes in Bio CBG plant engineering, anaerobic digestion, and compressed biogas technology. Lowering the carbon footprint of the energy sector with biomethane."
    active="home"
>
    <!-- HERO -->
    <section class="hero section" id="hero">
        <div class="hero__video-wrap" aria-hidden="true">
            <video class="hero__video" autoplay muted loop playsinline preload="metadata" poster="/hero-bg.webp">
                <source src="/hero-video.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
            </video>
        </div>

        <div class="hero__overlay"></div>

        <div class="container hero-content">
            <div class="hero__badge reveal-up">
                <span class="hero__badge-dot"></span>
                In Association with ARCIPLUG, Finland
            </div>
            <h1 class="hero-title reveal-text">Bio CBG Technology<br/>with Innovation</h1>
            <p class="hero__subtitle reveal-up">
                Lowering the carbon footprint of the energy sector with biomethane.
                Engineering sustainable solutions for a cleaner tomorrow.
            </p>
            <div class="hero__actions reveal-up">
                <a href="/services" class="btn btn--primary magnetic">Explore Solutions</a>
                <a href="/contact" class="btn btn--secondary magnetic">Contact Us</a>
            </div>

            <div class="hero__scroll-indicator" aria-hidden="true">
                <span>Scroll</span>
                <div class="hero__scroll-line"></div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ABOUT PREVIEW (Bento Grid) -->
    <section class="section about-preview" id="about">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="about-preview__intro">
                <div class="about-preview__intro-left">
                    <h2 class="reveal-text">Engineering the<br/>Energy Turnaround.</h2>
                </div>
                <div class="about-preview__intro-right">
                    <p class="about-preview__lead reveal-up">
                        We design and build biogas plants that convert organic waste into compressed biomethane — an immediately available, economically viable path to a low-carbon future for the energy sector.
                    </p>
                    <a href="/about" class="btn btn--ghost reveal-up">Discover the full story</a>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="about-bento">
                <div class="about-bento__cell about-bento__image reveal-blur">
                    <img src="/about-company.webp" alt="Uzzala Bio Energy reactor with green accent lighting" width="800" height="600" loading="lazy" decoding="async" />
                    <div class="about-bento__image-tag">
                        <span class="about-bento__image-tag-dot"></span>
                        Bio CBG Plant Engineering
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="about-bento__cell about-bento__stat about-bento__stat--top reveal-up">
                    <div class="about-bento__stat-num"><span class="counter" data-target="3" data-suffix="+">0</span></div>
                    <div class="about-bento__stat-label">Years engineering<br/>biogas systems</div>
                </div>

                <div class="about-bento__cell about-bento__stat about-bento__stat--bottom reveal-up">
                    <div class="about-bento__stat-num"><span class="counter" data-target="17" data-suffix="+">0</span></div>
                    <div class="about-bento__stat-label">Engineers and<br/>specialists on the team</div>
                </div>

                <div class="about-bento__cell about-bento__pillar reveal-up">
                    <div class="about-bento__pillar-icon">
                        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="6"/><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="2"/></svg>
                    </div>
                    <h4>Mission</h4>
                    <p>Produce world-class biogas products and services that accelerate the renewable energy transition.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="about-bento__cell about-bento__pillar reveal-up">
                    <div class="about-bento__pillar-icon">
                        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6"><path d="M2 12s3.5-7 10-7 10 7 10 7-3.5 7-10 7-10-7-10-7z"/><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3"/></svg>
                    </div>
                    <h4>Vision</h4>
                    <p>Lead the renewable energy movement with comprehensive, end-to-end clean energy solutions.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="about-bento__cell about-bento__pillar reveal-up">
                    <div class="about-bento__pillar-icon">
                        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6"><path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4"/><path d="M21 12c0 4.97-4.03 9-9 9s-9-4.03-9-9 4.03-9 9-9c2.39 0 4.68.94 6.36 2.64"/></svg>
                    </div>
                    <h4>Quality</h4>
                    <p>Every system is tested at every stage. No compromise on engineering integrity or material quality.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="about-bento__cell about-bento__partner reveal-up">
                    <div class="about-bento__partner-mark">
                        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M16 4h2a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v14a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H6a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V6a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h2"/><rect x="8" y="2" width="8" height="4" rx="1"/><path d="M9 14l2 2 4-4"/></svg>
                    </div>
                    <div class="about-bento__partner-text">
                        <span class="about-bento__partner-label">Strategic partnership</span>
                        <strong>ARCIPLUG, Finland</strong>
                        <span class="about-bento__partner-note">17+ years of dry anaerobic digestion expertise. Together we deliver Bio CBG plants engineered for Indian feedstock conditions.</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <div class="section-divider"></div>

    <!-- SERVICES GRID -->
    <section class="section services-section" id="services">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="services-section__header">
                <h2 class="reveal-text">Our Services & Solutions</h2>
                <p class="services-section__intro reveal-up">Eleven specialized capabilities across the four stages of the Bio-CBG value chain — from feedstock digestion to clean fuel delivery.</p>
            </div>

            <!-- GROUP 01: DIGESTION -->
            <div class="services-group" data-group="01">
                <header class="services-group__header">
                    <span class="services-group__index">01</span>
                    <div class="services-group__meta">
                        <h3 class="services-group__title">Digestion</h3>
                        <p class="services-group__caption">Anaerobic digesters that convert organic feedstock into raw biogas at industrial scale.</p>
                    </div>
                    <span class="services-group__rule" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                    <span class="services-group__count">02 systems</span>
                </header>
                <div class="services-bento services-bento--duo">
                    <a href="/services/plug-flow-digester" class="bento-card bento-card--feature">
                        <div class="bento-card__media">
                            <img src="/service-plug-flow.webp" alt="Plug Flow Digester system" width="800" height="500" loading="lazy" decoding="async" />
                        </div>
                        <div class="bento-card__body">
                            <span class="bento-card__tag">Arciplug® Dry AD</span>
                            <h4 class="bento-card__title">Plug Flow Digester</h4>
                            <p class="bento-card__text">3× higher loading rates with multi-feed flexibility — handles fibrous, dry, and high-solids feedstock.</p>
                            <span class="bento-card__cta">Explore <span aria-hidden="true">→</span></span>
                        </div>
                    </a>
                    <a href="/services/cstr-digester" class="bento-card bento-card--feature">
                        <div class="bento-card__media">
                            <img src="/service-cstr.webp" alt="CSTR Digester reactor vessel" width="800" height="500" loading="lazy" decoding="async" />
                        </div>
                        <div class="bento-card__body">
                            <span class="bento-card__tag">Mesophilic CSTR</span>
                            <h4 class="bento-card__title">CSTR Digester</h4>
                            <p class="bento-card__text">Continuous-stirred tank reactor at 32–38 °C with 10–12% organic loading and consistent biogas yield.</p>
                            <span class="bento-card__cta">Explore <span aria-hidden="true">→</span></span>
                        </div>
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- GROUP 02: PURIFICATION & UPGRADING -->
            <div class="services-group" data-group="02">
                <header class="services-group__header">
                    <span class="services-group__index">02</span>
                    <div class="services-group__meta">
                        <h3 class="services-group__title">Purification &amp; Upgrading</h3>
                        <p class="services-group__caption">Removing H₂S, CO₂, moisture, and inerts to produce pipeline-grade biomethane.</p>
                    </div>
                    <span class="services-group__rule" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                    <span class="services-group__count">04 systems</span>
                </header>
                <div class="services-bento services-bento--quad">
                    <a href="/services/h2s-removal-system" class="bento-card bento-card--compact">
                        <div class="bento-card__media">
                            <img src="/service-h2s.webp" alt="H2S Removal scrubber system" width="400" height="300" loading="lazy" decoding="async" />
                        </div>
                        <div class="bento-card__body">
                            <h4 class="bento-card__title">H₂S Removal System</h4>
                            <p class="bento-card__text">Caustic scrubber + bio reactor — 99%+ efficiency.</p>
                        </div>
                    </a>
                    <a href="/services/water-scrubber" class="bento-card bento-card--compact">
                        <div class="bento-card__media">
                            <img src="/service-water-scrubber.webp" alt="Water Scrubber absorption tower" width="400" height="300" loading="lazy" decoding="async" />
                        </div>
                        <div class="bento-card__body">
                            <h4 class="bento-card__title">Water Scrubber</h4>
                            <p class="bento-card__text">Counter-current column for CO₂ and H₂S absorption.</p>
                        </div>
                    </a>
                    <a href="/services/psa-purification-plant" class="bento-card bento-card--compact">
                        <div class="bento-card__media">
                            <img src="/service-psa.webp" alt="PSA Purification system" width="400" height="300" loading="lazy" decoding="async" />
                        </div>
                        <div class="bento-card__body">
                            <h4 class="bento-card__title">PSA Purification</h4>
                            <p class="bento-card__text">Adsorption vessels removing H₂O, CO₂, N₂ and O₂.</p>
                        </div>
                    </a>
                    <a href="/services/membrane-biogas-separation" class="bento-card bento-card--compact">
                        <div class="bento-card__media">
                            <img src="/service-membrane.webp" alt="Membrane biogas separation modules" width="400" height="300" loading="lazy" decoding="async" />
                        </div>
                        <div class="bento-card__body">
                            <h4 class="bento-card__title">Membrane Separation</h4>
                            <p class="bento-card__text">Polymer modules — 96.5–99% methane purity.</p>
                        </div>
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- GROUP 03: END PRODUCTS -->
            <div class="services-group" data-group="03">
                <header class="services-group__header">
                    <span class="services-group__index">03</span>
                    <div class="services-group__meta">
                        <h3 class="services-group__title">End Products</h3>
                        <p class="services-group__caption">Pipeline-quality biomethane, transport fuel, and organic fertilizer ready for market.</p>
                    </div>
                    <span class="services-group__rule" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                    <span class="services-group__count">03 outputs</span>
                </header>
                <div class="services-bento services-bento--trio">
                    <a href="/services/compressed-biogas" class="bento-card bento-card--hero">
                        <div class="bento-card__media">
                            <img src="/service-cbg.webp" alt="Compressed Biogas cylinders" width="800" height="600" loading="lazy" decoding="async" />
                        </div>
                        <div class="bento-card__body">
                            <span class="bento-card__tag">IS 16087:2016 Certified</span>
                            <h4 class="bento-card__title">Compressed Biogas (CBG)</h4>
                            <p class="bento-card__text">97% methane purity, free from liquids and particulates — ready for grid injection or transport.</p>
                            <span class="bento-card__cta">Explore <span aria-hidden="true">→</span></span>
                        </div>
                    </a>
                    <a href="/services/cbg-fuel" class="bento-card bento-card--compact">
                        <div class="bento-card__media">
                            <img src="/service-cbg-fuel.webp" alt="CBG fuel dispensing station" width="400" height="300" loading="lazy" decoding="async" />
                        </div>
                        <div class="bento-card__body">
                            <h4 class="bento-card__title">CBG Fuel</h4>
                            <p class="bento-card__text">Clean transport fuel — lower emissions, lower cost.</p>
                        </div>
                    </a>
                    <a href="/services/organic-fertilizer" class="bento-card bento-card--compact">
                        <div class="bento-card__media">
                            <img src="/service-organic-fertilizer.webp" alt="Organic Fertilizer" width="400" height="300" loading="lazy" decoding="async" />
                        </div>
                        <div class="bento-card__body">
                            <h4 class="bento-card__title">Organic Fertilizer</h4>
                            <p class="bento-card__text">Plant stimulator and bio-fungicide from digestate.</p>
                        </div>
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- GROUP 04: APPLICATIONS -->
            <div class="services-group" data-group="04">
                <header class="services-group__header">
                    <span class="services-group__index">04</span>
                    <div class="services-group__meta">
                        <h3 class="services-group__title">Applications</h3>
                        <p class="services-group__caption">Turnkey deployments for waste management, sewage, and feedstock-specific energy plants.</p>
                    </div>
                    <span class="services-group__rule" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                    <span class="services-group__count">02 deployments</span>
                </header>
                <div class="services-bento services-bento--duo">
                    <a href="/services/sewage-treatment-plant" class="bento-card bento-card--feature">
                        <div class="bento-card__media">
                            <img src="/service-sewage.webp" alt="Sewage Treatment Plant" width="800" height="500" loading="lazy" decoding="async" />
                        </div>
                        <div class="bento-card__body">
                            <span class="bento-card__tag">Municipal scale</span>
                            <h4 class="bento-card__title">Sewage Treatment Plant</h4>
                            <p class="bento-card__text">Anaerobic digestion of municipal sewage sludge with 80–85% biogas yield in 15–18 days.</p>
                            <span class="bento-card__cta">Explore <span aria-hidden="true">→</span></span>
                        </div>
                    </a>
                    <a href="/services/biogas-from-waste" class="bento-card bento-card--feature">
                        <div class="bento-card__media">
                            <img src="/service-biogas-waste.webp" alt="Biogas from organic waste feedstock" width="800" height="500" loading="lazy" decoding="async" />
                        </div>
                        <div class="bento-card__body">
                            <span class="bento-card__tag">Multi-feedstock</span>
                            <h4 class="bento-card__title">Biogas From Waste</h4>
                            <p class="bento-card__text">Pressmud, cow dung, poultry, kitchen waste, and MSW all converted into clean energy.</p>
                            <span class="bento-card__cta">Explore <span aria-hidden="true">→</span></span>
                        </div>
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- CUSTOM SOLUTION CTA -->
            <a href="/contact" class="services-cta magnetic">
                <div class="services-cta__left">
                    <span class="services-cta__eyebrow">Custom Solutions</span>
                    <h3 class="services-cta__title">Don't see your feedstock or capacity?<span>We engineer turnkey Bio-CBG plants tailored to any site.</span></h3>
                </div>
                <div class="services-cta__right">
                    <span class="services-cta__link">Talk to our engineers</span>
                    <span class="services-cta__arrow" aria-hidden="true">
                        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
                            <path d="M5 12h14M13 5l7 7-7 7"/>
                        </svg>
                    </span>
                </div>
            </a>
        </div>
    </section>

    <div class="section-divider"></div>

    <!-- PROCESS TIMELINE -->
    <section class="section process-section" id="process">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="process-section__header">
                <h2 class="reveal-scramble">From Waste to Energy</h2>
                <p class="process-section__intro reveal-up">Four stages turn organic waste into pipeline-grade renewable fuel. Scroll to follow the energy.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="process-timeline" data-active-step="0">
                <svg class="process-flow" viewBox="0 0 100 1000" preserveAspectRatio="none" aria-hidden="true">
                    <defs>
                        <linearGradient id="flow-gradient" x1="0" y1="0" x2="0" y2="1">
                            <stop offset="0%" stop-color="#39ff14"/>
                            <stop offset="100%" stop-color="#00f0ff"/>
                        </linearGradient>
                        <filter id="flow-glow">
                            <feGaussianBlur stdDeviation="3" result="blur"/>
                            <feMerge>
                                <feMergeNode in="blur"/>
                                <feMergeNode in="SourceGraphic"/>
                            </feMerge>
                        </filter>
                    </defs>
                    <path class="process-flow__track" d="M50,0 C30,180 70,320 50,500 C30,680 70,820 50,1000" fill="none" stroke="rgba(255,255,255,0.08)" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/>
                    <path class="process-flow__path" d="M50,0 C30,180 70,320 50,500 C30,680 70,820 50,1000" fill="none" stroke="url(#flow-gradient)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" filter="url(#flow-glow)"/>
                    <circle class="process-flow__particle" r="6" fill="#39ff14" filter="url(#flow-glow)"/>
                </svg>

                <article class="process-step" id="step-01" data-step-index="0" data-stage="collection">
                    <div class="process-step__node" aria-hidden="true"><span class="process-step__node-dot"></span></div>
                    <div class="process-step__number" data-target="1">00</div>
                    <div class="process-step__image">
                        <img src="/process-step1.webp" alt="Agricultural waste collection at industrial yard" width="500" height="350" loading="lazy" decoding="async" />
                        <span class="process-step__stat">6+ feedstock types</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="process-step__content">
                        <span class="process-step__eyebrow">Stage 01 — Intake</span>
                        <h3 class="process-step__title">Waste Collection</h3>
                        <p class="process-step__text">Organic feedstock — pressmud, sugarcane bagasse, cow dung, poultry waste, kitchen waste, and municipal solid waste — is collected and transported to the plant.</p>
                    </div>
                </article>

                <article class="process-step" id="step-02" data-step-index="1" data-stage="digestion">
                    <div class="process-step__node" aria-hidden="true"><span class="process-step__node-dot"></span></div>
                    <div class="process-step__number" data-target="2">00</div>
                    <div class="process-step__image">
                        <img src="/process-step2.webp" alt="Anaerobic digester tank with methane gas" width="500" height="350" loading="lazy" decoding="async" />
                        <span class="process-step__stat">32–38°C mesophilic</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="process-step__content">
                        <span class="process-step__eyebrow">Stage 02 — Conversion</span>
                        <h3 class="process-step__title">Anaerobic Digestion</h3>
                        <p class="process-step__text">Feedstock is processed in sealed digester tanks where microorganisms break down organic matter in the absence of oxygen, producing raw biogas rich in methane.</p>
                    </div>
                </article>

                <article class="process-step" id="step-03" data-step-index="2" data-stage="purification">
                    <div class="process-step__node" aria-hidden="true"><span class="process-step__node-dot"></span></div>
                    <div class="process-step__number" data-target="3">00</div>
                    <div class="process-step__image">
                        <img src="/process-step3.webp" alt="Gas purification membrane system" width="500" height="350" loading="lazy" decoding="async" />
                        <span class="process-step__stat">97%+ methane purity</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="process-step__content">
                        <span class="process-step__eyebrow">Stage 03 — Refinement</span>
                        <h3 class="process-step__title">Gas Purification</h3>
                        <p class="process-step__text">Raw biogas is purified through H₂S removal, water scrubbing, PSA, and membrane separation to achieve 97%+ methane purity — IS 16087:2016 compliant.</p>
                    </div>
                </article>

                <article class="process-step" id="step-04" data-step-index="3" data-stage="distribution">
                    <div class="process-step__node" aria-hidden="true"><span class="process-step__node-dot"></span></div>
                    <div class="process-step__number" data-target="4">00</div>
                    <div class="process-step__image">
                        <img src="/process-step4.webp" alt="CBG cylinders loaded on distribution trucks" width="500" height="350" loading="lazy" decoding="async" />
                        <span class="process-step__stat">IS 16087:2016</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="process-step__content">
                        <span class="process-step__eyebrow">Stage 04 — Delivery</span>
                        <h3 class="process-step__title">CBG Distribution</h3>
                        <p class="process-step__text">Compressed Biogas is stored in high-pressure cylinders and distributed to fueling stations, industrial consumers, and the gas grid — clean, renewable, carbon-negative fuel.</p>
                    </div>
                </article>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <div class="section-divider"></div>

    <!-- ORGANIC FERTILIZER -->
    <section class="section fertilizer-section" id="fertilizer">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="fertilizer-section__grid">
                <div class="fertilizer-section__content">
                    <h2 class="reveal-text">Organic Fertilizer</h2>
                    <p class="reveal-up">
                        The sludge from biogas production can be used as organic fertilizer which functions as plant growth stimulator and bio-fungicide. Biogas residue fertilizer is not only with high quality, but also a good soil conditioner.
                    </p>
                    <p class="reveal-up">
                        According to the determination, applying biogas organic fertilizer can increase soil 0.17-0.6% of organic matter content, enhance 0.003-0.005% of total nitrogen and improve 0.01-0.03% of total phosphorus.
                    </p>

                    <div class="fertilizer-tabs reveal-up">
                        <button class="fertilizer-tab active" data-tab="organic">Organic Fertilizer</button>
                        <button class="fertilizer-tab" data-tab="advantages">Advantages</button>
                        <button class="fertilizer-tab" data-tab="benefits">Benefits</button>
                    </div>
                    <div class="fertilizer-tab-content active" id="tab-organic">
                        <p>Using sludge from biogas production as a high-quality organic soil enhancement. Natural, sustainable, and chemical-free.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="fertilizer-tab-content" id="tab-advantages">
                        <p>Improves soil structure, increases water retention, enhances nutrient availability, and promotes microbial activity in the soil ecosystem.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="fertilizer-tab-content" id="tab-benefits">
                        <p>Reduces dependency on chemical fertilizers, lowers agricultural costs, closes the waste-to-value loop, and creates an additional revenue stream.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="fertilizer-section__media reveal-clip">
                    <video autoplay muted loop playsinline preload="metadata" poster="/fertilizer-section.webp">
                        <source src="/organic-video.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
                    </video>
                    <img src="/fertilizer-section.webp" alt="Lush green organic farm field at golden hour" width="600" height="400" loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="fertilizer-section__fallback" />
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- STATS -->
    <section class="section stats-section" id="stats">
        <div class="stats-section__video-wrap" aria-hidden="true">
            <video autoplay muted loop playsinline preload="metadata">
                <source src="/stats-video.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
            </video>
        </div>
        <div class="stats-section__overlay"></div>

        <div class="container">
            <div class="stats-grid">
                <div class="stat-item">
                    <div class="stat-item__number counter" data-target="3" data-suffix="+">0</div>
                    <div class="stat-item__label">Years<br/>Experience</div>
                </div>
                <div class="stat-item">
                    <div class="stat-item__number counter" data-target="3" data-suffix="+">0</div>
                    <div class="stat-item__label">Ongoing<br/>Biogas Projects</div>
                </div>
                <div class="stat-item">
                    <div class="stat-item__number counter" data-target="1" data-suffix="+">0</div>
                    <div class="stat-item__label">Projects<br/>Completed</div>
                </div>
                <div class="stat-item">
                    <div class="stat-item__number counter" data-target="17" data-suffix="+">0</div>
